subject: Physical Day Pass Purchase
content: Hello,I work for a non profit and we are trying to purchase day bus passes for the women in job training. We would like to have physicalpasses so that we can distribute them to the women when they are needed. Could you please let me know howI can go about making this purchase.Thank you for your time!Kind Regards,Sierra AdkinsOffice ManagerSanctuary Project2301 E. Cesar Chavez St., Austin TX 78702Registered 501c3 Non-Profitwww.SanctuaryProject.com512-991-2029
